====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# {{lb|zh|literary|obsolete}} [[torrential]]
# {{lb|zh|literary|or|dialectal}} [[turbid]]
# to [[mix]]; to [[blend]]
#: {{zh-x|搞混|to confuse (two things); to mix up}}
