#: {{zh-x|把 紅豆 和 綠豆 混 在 一起|to mix red beans and green beans}}
# to [[pass off]] as
#: {{zh-x|魚目混珠|to pass off fake products as genuine|lit=to pass off fish eyes as pearls}}
