# to [[muddle along]]
#: {{zh-x|混日子{zi}|to muck around; to drift through the days}}
# to [[get along]] with somebody
#: {{zh-x|我 很 快 就 跟 他們 混 熟 了。|I quickly became familiar with them.}}
#: {{zh-x|別 跟 流氓 混 在 一起。|Stop hanging out with hooligans.}}
# [[thoughtlessly]]; [[casually]]
# {{lb|zh|literary}} to [[unite]]; to [[combine]]
# {{lb|zh|literary}} to [[stir up]] trouble; to [[throw]] into [[disorder]]; to [[disrupt]]
# {{lb|zh|Teochew}} to [[disturb]] (someone)
# {{lb|zh|literary}} to [[joke]]
